@startuml
actor "车辆仿真系统" as Simulator
participant "车辆运行时服务" as Runtime
participant "车辆运行时管理器" as Manager
participant "单车运行时实例" as Instance
participant "车辆控制队列" as ControlQueue
participant "中央列车管理" as TrainManager
participant "中央状态镜像" as Mirror

Simulator -> Runtime: 请求启动列车实例(列车标识、编组参数)
activate Runtime
Runtime -> Manager: 启动列车实例()
activate Manager
Manager -> Instance: 创建或获取实例
activate Instance
Instance -> ControlQueue: 唤醒控制队列()
activate ControlQueue
ControlQueue --> Instance: 控制实例就绪
deactivate ControlQueue
Instance --> Manager: 实例状态
deactivate Instance
Manager -> TrainManager: 注册中央列车镜像(列车标识、链路标识、初始位置)
activate TrainManager
TrainManager -> Mirror: 创建 TrainEntity 和 CONNECTING 会话
activate Mirror
Mirror --> TrainManager: 镜像状态
deactivate Mirror
TrainManager --> Manager: 注册结果
deactivate TrainManager
Manager --> Runtime: 启动完成
deactivate Manager
Runtime --> Simulator: 返回运行时实例状态
deactivate Runtime
@enduml
